name: Signed Range Dominican Corona
additionalNotes: There are two versions of the Dunhill Signed Range. This original version was manufactured in the Dominican Republic from 2003-2007, but can still be found in shops.  This cigar has Dunhill in block print caps, whereas the newer Nicaraguan version has the Dunhill name in cursive, surmounted with a crest and with "since 1907" below.
